<div class=3D"keyconcept">
  <h5 id=3D"#section12" class=3D"section-heading">Key Concept: Accuracy of =
the Fourth Order Runge-Kutta Algorithm</h5>
  <p class=3D"center">The global error of the Fourth Order Runge-Kutta algo=
rithm is <em>O(h<sup>4</sup>)</em>. <br>
  This is not proven here, but the proof is similar to that for the Second =
Order Runge-Kutta</p>
</div>
